    "body": "This PR enables Link Time Optimization (LTO), configures more appropriate memory and stack limits, enables Asyncify and exception handling, and restores strict undefined-symbol checking to ensure missing dependencies are caught during linking. \r\n\r\nIt also introduces a `wasm_stubs.c` implementation that provides Emscripten compatible replacements for a number of libuv and platform specific functions that are not available in a WASM environment. ",
